data.value: Tetris Mania is a game created during my college career as a class final project. Within the game you can choose to play Classic Tetris with "naive" gravity where blocks will only fall a distance equal to the number of rows completed below them. Additionally you can play "cascade" Tetris, where the blocks will fall to their maximum distance! Enjoy and make sure to read either the details or the README.txt found with this game for basic controls and more!
